<p>THE HOTEL IS ALSO IDEALLY LOCATED CLOSE TO AN ARRAY OF PREMIUM BUSINESS AND TOURIST ATTRACTIONS, SUCH AS SHANGHAI DISNEYLAND, HAICHANG OCEAN PARK AND SHANGHAI WILD ANIMAL PARK. FOR INTERNATIONAL GUESTS, THE HOTEL IS 25-MINUTE DRIVE AWAY FROM SHANGHAI PUDONG INTERNATIONAL AIRPORT.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200918/5601fc3e289c41aa9f6198a02df38588.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200918/2d8a1e685bf04d1189e0416ef5b0357c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200918/5fd7cb1b14944fc4b4b315640534ccfa.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>中优集团</strong>与美国<strong>孩之宝</strong>公司战略授权合作，将在本项目打造全球首个“<strong>变形金刚</strong>”和“<strong>小马宝莉</strong>”两个IP主题的亲子主题客房、室内亲子乐园和配套商业，将于明年全面整体开业。</p>
<p>AUTHORIZED BY HASBRO, “TRANSFORMERS” AND “MY LITTLE PONY” IP THEME GUEST ROOMS, INDOOR PARENT-CHILD PARADISE AND ESSENTIAL COMMERCIAL FACILITIES THAT WILL OPEN IN NEXT YEAR.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200918/0ea36d2c76274168876b7a188e4ad22a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>从浦东新区充满活力的绿色自然景观中汲取灵感，酒店旨在打造为现代城市休闲度假的理想之地，将宾客与自然紧密相联。采用原木、大理石、织物、皮革以及当地生产的麻绳等天然物料搭配定制家具和几何造型灯饰，营造出一方悠闲惬意且趣意盎然并存的美学空间。</p>
<p>DRAWING INSPIRATION FROM THE VIBRANT ENERGY AND LUSH GREENERY OF PUDONG DISTRICT, THE HOTEL IS DESIGNED TO CREATE A CONTEMPORARY URBAN RETREAT THAT CONNECTS GUESTS WITH NATURE.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200918/4bf1245b53bc466fa5f8d358d9d934a1.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>复古可爱的<strong>户外有轨小火车</strong>每日欢乐发车，怀旧主题场景布置及背景音乐，电力系统匠人纯手工打造，环形轨道徜徉在中优城市广场商业综合体，每一个单程约5-8分钟，沿途绿树成荫、溪流潺潺，穿过街上人群欢声笑语，路过五光十色的橱窗，邂逅该区域的明星——两只巨型气球的小马宝莉，在童趣和玩乐之间切换自如。</p>
<p>OUTDOOR LITTLE TRAIN OF VINTAGE THEME DECORATION PARKING AT THE FRONT OF HOTEL MAIN ENTRANCE, GUEST COULD ENJOY VIVID SCENERY ALONG THE RAIL TO EXPERIENCE JOYFUL FAMILY STAYCATION.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200918/7f4e35298e964d7b9dbe61ba5cf81829.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200918/8aeaf15532c8457484dda96bcf8fcda9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200918/51a6b49fb85b4860800224c04328a6a5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>241间精心设计的客房兼具功能、时尚、舒适于一体，意在打造创意工作空间，均配备圆形办公桌、躺椅休息区、咖啡桌及步入式衣柜，透过全景落地窗，宾客可在此欣赏城市天际线。并配备高速无线网络，万豪酒店特色床品及高清电视等一系列设施。<strong>亲子房</strong>配备整套儿童专属礼遇，从浴袍、摇椅、玩具、配色板、迷你帐篷，到卡通主题床品、贴纸及儿童沐浴用品一应俱全，确保全家乐享童趣悠闲的亲子时光。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">THE 241 WELL-APPOINTED GUESTROOMS ALL FEATURE A ROUND OFFICE DESK, A SITTING AREA COMPLETE WITH A CHAISE LONGUE AND A COFFEE TABLE. FAMILY ROOMS FEATURE A COMPLETE SET OF CHILD-FRIENDLY AMENITIES FROM BATHROBE, TOYS, MINI TENT TO CARTOON-THEMED BEDDING, STICKERS, AND BATH AMENITIES FOR KIDS.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200918/1f828d99fe9c4f1c8c88291c473333c2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>3个各具特色的餐厅及1个大堂酒廊，为宾客呈现万豪品牌特色的餐饮体验。贡厨全日制餐厅(GOJI KITCHEN + BAR) 提供全日零点菜单及一系列西式及亚洲风味精选自助美食；<strong>万豪中餐厅</strong>（MAN HO）主理地道粤菜及上海本地菜，设有7间雅致的私人包房，是商务用餐及亲友相聚的理想之选；雾山（SMOKI MOTO）特色餐厅具有现代都市风格，主打精致韩式烧烤及寿司；大堂酒廊（THE LOUNGE）秉持万豪品牌备受赞誉的大堂吧理念，为商务会议或休闲聚会提供时尚舒适之所。</p>
<p>THE HOTEL FEATURES THREE STYLISH DINING VENUES AND A LOBBY LOUNGE. ALL-DAY RESTAURANT GOJI KITCHEN BAR SERVES AN À LA CARTE MENU AND A SUMPTUOUS BUFFET; MAN HO CHINESE RESTAURANT OFFERS THE BRAND’S AUTHENTIC CANTONESE CULINARY EXPERIENCE WITH A TOUCH OF SHANGHAI; SMOKI MOTO FEATURES KOREAN BARBEQUE AND GOURMET SUSHI; WHILE THE GREATROOM, WHICH IS MARRIOTT HOTEL’S RENOWNED LOBBY LOUNGE CONCEPT, PROVIDING A MODERN, COMFORTABLE GATHERING SPOT FOR BUSINESS AND LEISURE MEETINGS.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200918/af1e3153daf44b20be300393cdb21164.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200918/e9fc1228aad74f3cad36d5c21452dff3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200918/5b8fd9b3715d423d89345c217d2320c9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200918/e316b45099bb40e29d34ae10ead3a9d7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>总面积达2,650平方米的会议及宴会空间，是举办各类会议和活动的理想场所，无柱式800平方米大宴会厅和400平方米的宴会厅适合举办大型会议及宴会，6个多功能厅适合举办不同规模的商务活动、私人派对及独特而难忘的婚宴。24小时健身中心，助力宾客在此放松身心，尽享悠闲时光。</p>
<p>WITH A TOTAL OF 2,650 SQUARE-METERS, THE HOTEL IS AN IDEAL VENUE FOR EVERY KIND OF EVENT AND MEETING. THE PILLARLESS 800-SQUARE-METER GRAND BALLROOM AND 400-SQUARE-METER JUNIOR BALLROOM OFFER IDEAL SPACES FOR LARGE CONFERENCES AND LAVISH GATHERINGS, WHILE THE 6 DIFFERENT FUNCTION ROOMS CAN HOST BUSINESS EVENTS AND PRIVATE PARTIES OF ALL STYLES AND SCALES, AS WELL AS GLAMOROUS WEDDINGS. TO HELP GUESTS RELAX AND UNWIND AFTER A PRODUCTIVE WORKDAY OR AN EXHILARATING PRIVATE EVENT, THE HOTEL OFFERS 24-HOUR FITNESS CENTER.</p>
